  "instructions": [
    "Combine softened butter and flour in a large bowl and mix until well combined.",
    "Add shredded coconut and mix until the mixture resembles coarse crumbs.",
    "In a separate bowl, whip chilled coconut cream until stiff peaks form.",
    "Add sun-dried tomatoes, parsley, garlic, salt, and black pepper to the coconut cream and mix until well combined.",
    "Add the coconut cream mixture to the coconut-butter mixture and mix until a smooth fondue forms.",
    "Transfer the fondue to a fondue pot and heat over low heat.",
    "Serve the fondue with crumbled feta cheese and fresh parsley on the side."
